<P>
   FOR SOME 4th GRADERS, THERE'S MORE TO LIFE THAN A TEST &QL;
</P>
<P>
   A0569 BC-TEST-TEX EDITORS: This is a test from the Fort Worth
Star-Telegram. 11 23:47 U A
</P>
<P>
   A0566 BC-OBIT-RELLY-NYT 661 23:45 U A
</P>
<P>
   GAVIN RELLY, 72, DIES; HELPED END APARTHEID &QL;
</P>
<P>
   A0563 BC-HIVTESTS-INTERNET-SFCHRON 1509 23:35 R A
</P>
<P>
   HIV SELF-TEST KITS WORRY HEALTH EXPERTS
