  BEST SELLERS:
HARDCOVER BOOKS   (For release on Sunday, Jan. 17.)  (Eds: This
file is the full version of the best-seller list that includes how
many weeks each book has been on the list and where the book stood
the previous week. Please see BESTSELLERS-HARD-S-NYT for an
abbreviated format.)  (mk) 
