hardly a rarity in Hollywood - but with the release of
``HurlyBurly,'' on Friday, starring husband and wife team Sean Penn
and Robin Wright Penn, we thought we'd take a look at some of the
better ones. (Ringel, Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
</P>
