``Maurice Sendak's Little Bear: Friends,'' $9.95.
</P>
<P>
   Black History Month: ``Cabin in the Sky,'' ``The Defiant Ones,''
``Lilies of the Field,'' ``A Patch of Blue.'' $19.98. ``In the Heat
of the Night,'' ``A Family Thing,'' ``The Organization,'' ``They
Call Me Mr. Tibbs,'' $14.95.
</P>
<P>
   Soul Cinema: ``Cotton Comes to Harlem,'' ``I'm Gonna Git You
Sucka,'' ``Shaft,'' ``Shaft's Big Score,'' ``Shaft in
Africa,''``Norman, Is That You?'' $14.95.
</P>
