EDITORS: 
  
</HEADLINE>
  
 (Refiling for those needing)  
 Wednesday, Jan. 13, 1999
<TEXT>
<P>
   The Hearst News Service will file the following stories for
Thursday. If you have questions, please call Tim Spence at
202-298-6920. &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR;  &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   (Slugline includes the ``HNS'' tag.)
