<DATE_TIME> 1999-01-13 13:43 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1328 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-FUNDS-QUARTER-BOS &LR;      01-13 1195
