<DATE_TIME> 1999-01-13 14:09 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1354 &Cx1f; tth-z
r l &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-BOOKSTORES-MAIL-SPI &LR;      01-13 1335
