<P>
   FBN-BRONCOS (Denver) _ John Elway, who finally won the Super
Bowl last season and is the city's most famous athlete, might be
playing his last game on Sunday. By Joe Drape.
</P>
<P>
   HKN-RANGERS-ISLANDERS (New York) _ Islanders at Rangers, 7:30
p.m. By Joe Lapointe.
