<HEADER>
A1582 &Cx1f; ttj-z
u v &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-HEARST-NEWS-BUDGET-1S     01-13 0727
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-HEARST-NEWS-BUDGET-1STLD-WRITETHRU-HNS </SLUG>
  
 Wednesday, Jan. 13, 1998    
 Editors     
<TEXT>
<P>
