<P>
   BASKETBALL
</P>
<P>
   NBA
</P>
<P>
   BKN-JORDAN _ CHICAGO _ Coverage of Michael Jordan's retirement
announcement, with scene, mood, reaction. (Bunn, Atlanta
Journal-Constitutuiion)
</P>
<P>
   w/BKN-JORDAN-NUHN _ DAYTON _ Columnist Gary Nuhn comments on
Jordan's departure and looks at what's next for the NBA. (Nuhn,
Dayton Daily News). 17.
</P>
<P>
   BKN-JORDAN-ARCH _ LAS VEGAS _ Trying to get reaction from Mike
Tyson and other Vegas high rollers on Jordan's announcement.
(Archdeacon, Dayton Daily News). 25.
</P>
<P>
   BKN-JORDAN-STODA _ Greg began watching and reporting on Jordan
in high school while both were living in North Carolina . . . he
takes us through
</P>
<P>
   the years (Greg Stoda, Palm Beach Post). 21.
</P>
<P>
   BKN-JORDAN-GEORGE _ Dave George column on Jordan, possibly
through eyes of Heat announcer, former coach Jack Ramsay, who was
part of team that passed on Jordan in the draft. (George, Palm
Beach Post). 18.
</P>
<P>
   BKN-JORDAN-ANALYSIS _ Analysis: With Jordan gone and the Bulls
down, which teams will step up? (D'Angelo, Palm Beach Post). 15.
</P>
<P>
   BKN-PAXSON _ DAYTON _ Kettering, Ohio native John Paxson and
Dayton product Ron Harper won NBA championships with Michael
Jordan. We ask them to reflect on playing - and winning - with
Michael. (Katz, Dayton Daily News). 15.
</P>
