   Paired with the lead story, both under a two-column hed:
</P>
<P>
   BRAZIL-U.S. (Washington) _ A look at the impact of the Brazilian
economic crisis in Washington. By David E. Sanger. (Scheduled to
move by 9 p.m. ET in ``f'' news file.)
</P>
<P>
   Top center: 2-column Michael Jordan photo; stories inside
Sports.
</P>
<P>
   Off-lead story:
</P>
<P>
   IMPEACH-RDP (Washington) _ New details emerge about what Senate
Republican leaders are preparing for in the next phase of the
impeachment trial. By Eric Schmitt. (Scheduled to move by 9:30 p.m.
ET in ``w'' news file.)
</P>
