<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-MICROSOFT14-1STLEDE-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    WITNESS: MICROSOFT LACKS MONOPOLY POWER
 &HT;    Eds: corrects spelling of ``reverse'' in final graf.
 &HT;    Moving in (f) financial and (w) Washington queues
