<HEADLINE>
LANDMARK ENTERTAINMENT BRINGING CIRCUS TO CALIFORNIA TRIBAL CASINO
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
BY DAVE MCNARY  
 c.1999 Los Angeles Daily News  
<TEXT>
